sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(Platform Ingress)
    participant LS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Inference<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant VecDB as Vector DB<br/>(Milvus/pgvector/Qdrant)
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>HTTP
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FMS as TrustyAI FMS<br/>HTTP/HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,PG: Flow 1: Chat Completion Request (vLLM backend)
        Client->>LS: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP, no app-level auth<br/>(platform auth at ingress)
        LS->>vLLM: Forward inference request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Bearer Token<br/>(VLLM_API_TOKEN)
        vLLM-->>LS: Inference response
        LS->>PG: Log inference<br/>PostgreSQL wire protocol<br/>Password auth (POSTGRES_PASSWORD)
        LS-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,VecDB: Flow 2: RAG Query with Vector Search
        Client->>LS: POST /v1/agents/*<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
        LS->>VecDB: Vector similarity search<br/>REST/gRPC/PostgreSQL<br/>API Key / Password auth
        VecDB-->>LS: Relevant documents
        LS->>vLLM: Augmented inference request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Bearer Token
        vLLM-->>LS: Inference response
        LS->>PG: Log agent state + inference<br/>PostgreSQL, Password
        LS-->>Client: Augmented response<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Evaluation via Kubeflow Pipeline (RAGAS remote)
        Client->>LS: POST /v1/eval/*<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
        LS->>KFP: Submit evaluation pipeline<br/>HTTP, Bearer Token<br/>(KUBEFLOW_PIPELINES_TOKEN)
        KFP->>S3: Store/retrieve eval data<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, AWS IAM
        S3-->>KFP: Evaluation artifacts
        KFP->>LS: Callback with results<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
        LS-->>Client: Evaluation results<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over Client,FMS: Flow 4: Safety Check via TrustyAI FMS
        Client->>LS: POST /v1/safety/*<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
        LS->>FMS: Safety shield evaluation<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, configurable SSL<br/>(FMS_SSL_CERT_PATH)
        FMS-->>LS: Safety verdict
        LS-->>Client: Safety check result<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    end
